well. The white king is pretty vulnerable.}) 14... Bxc3 15. bxc3 Nc2 16. Qxc4
Nxe1 17. Bf4 Bb5 18. Bxe5 Bxc4 19. Rxe1 Ne8 $15 {[%cal Gf7f6,Ge6e5,Ge8d6]
Black is still slightly better due to White's vulnerable pawn structure. The
next moves are ...f7-f6 followed by . ..e6-e5, and ...Nd6. Nevertheless, the
