Another thematic idea would be} 10... Nd5 11. Qxc4 Bf6 {[%csl Ra1,Rb1,Rc1] As
we know, Black wants to prevent White's queenside development. Nevertheless,
after} 12. Na3 Ba6 13. Qb3 {[%cal Ga3c4,Gc4e3] it turns out that White is
