25. Bd7 Rd8 $11 {with a draw.}) 20... cxd3 21. Bc6 g5 22. Bxd7 gxf4 23. Bxh3
fxe3 24. Re2 dxe2 $11 {The draw is obvious.}) 11... Ba6 {[%csl Gc4] Now, Black
