{[%evp 0,28,18,24,30,17,7,18,17,5,5,3,3,23,11,11,11,-13,10,10,34,-8,20,24,39,
-2,9,8,18,7,16]} 1. d4 Nf6 2. c4 e6 3. Nf3 d5 4. g3 Be7 5. Bg2 O-O 6. O-O dxc4
7. Ne5 c5 8. dxc5 Qc7 9. Nxc4 Rd8 10. Qb3 {Putting pressure on b7 and planning
