huge advantage since White has problems developing the queenside.}) 11... Nd4
12. Bxd4 Rxd4 {This is probably the most important crossroads for the
evaluation of the entire line. On the next move, Black is going to win the
c5-pawn back. The g2-bishop is White's biggest asset in the position. As I
