least some pressure. Black should reckon with moves like Rxa6 followed by Nc6
or Nc6 immediately. Nevertheless, the energetic} c3 $1 {marks the beginning of
a forced sequence leading to a favourable position for Black.} 14. Qxc3 Rc8 15.
Qb2 Rc2 16. Qb1 Qxd4 17. Ndf3 Qc3 $15 {White still needs to find compensation
