} ({The alternative} 8. Nc3 Qxb3 9. axb3 Nc6 10. dxc5 Bxc5 {is just a
transposition.}) 8... Qxb3 9. axb3 Nc6 10. Nc3 Bxc5 {is just a transposition.}
11. O-O e5 {Black's good central control and superior pawn structure balance
