} 18. Nxe4 $2 Nxe4 19. Bxe4 Nxa7 20. Rxa7 Bc5 21. Ra4 b5 $17 {when Black is
winning material.}) 18... Bb4 {[%cal Gh7h6,Gg7g5]} 19. h4 h6 20. Nh3 Nd5 $44 {
The activity of the black pieces provides more than enough compensation for
