) ({One of Gelfand's pet sidelines is} 6. Qd3 $5 {Just like after 6.Qc2 and 6.
Qb3, White protects the c4-pawn in advance. This time, however, he keeps good
control of the important d4-square. Therefore, the advance ...c7-c5 is less
