in view of} Nb4 17. Bxb4 Bxb4 18. Nd2 dxe4 19. Bxe4 Bxe4 20. Rxe4 Qf5 $17 {
when White is in trouble.}) {A possible follow-up would be} 14... b5 15. Qd1
dxe4 16. Rxe4 Qd7 {[%cal Ga8d8,Ge7f6]} 17. b3 {White should play very
